title: Pakistan China Trade & Investment Forum held in Beijing
snippet: Zhang Chunxian, vice chairman of the National People's Congress Standing Committee, attends the Pakistan China Trade & Investment Forum in Beijing, capital of China, April 28, 2019. Pakistani Prime Minister Imran Khan (3rd R), who was in Beijng to attend the Second Belt and Road Forum for International Cooperation, attended the Pakistan China Trade & Investment Forum. (Xinhua/Wen Guixu)
